generalmodalmodel.name: Art exhibition - digital art pieces
generalmodalmodel.descrition: In order to promote our team and most importantly - our iGEM project to the public, our team organized the second annual Scientific Art Exhibition and Escape room. The event consisted of several parts, one of which was exhibiting art pieces created by team members themselves in the process of wet lab work. Except for our own art pieces we received and exhibited photographs from several other teams and put them on display for event visitors to see and appreciate beautiful moments of long hour work captured in frames.

generalmodalmodel.name: xuinya
generalmodalmodel.descrition: There is a reason why we call our team's primary PI the boss. no photosession happens without him. He is our major sponsor and mentor, lets us use his lab in the Institute of Technology of University of Tartu, thus the shots are being called by him.
